OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772132672
OL,3,CPlans to turn reservoir into a
OL,4,C'holiday resort' rejected by planners
OL,6,FPlans to build holiday units at Bewl
OL,7,FWater, turning the reservoir site into
OL,8,Fa tourist attraction, have been
OL,9,Funanimously rejected by Wealden
OL,10,FDistrict Council's planning committee.
OL,12,FIt follows warnings from wildlife
OL,13,Fexperts that light pollution from the
OL,14,Fdevelopment of 11 apartments would
OL,15,Fdrive away the thousands of gulls that
OL,16,Froost on the water there.
OL,18,FCouncillors said they were
OL,19,F'unconvinced' about the use of light-
OL,20,Flimiting 'smart glass' proposed by the
OL,21,Fdevelopers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
