FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772132672
OL,3,CPlans to turn reservoir into a
OL,4,C'holiday resort' rejected by planners
OL,6,FThe scheme had been recommended for
OL,7,Fapproval by council officers.
OL,9,FIt follows pleas from Olympic Gold
OL,10,Fmedallist, rower Emily Craig, who
OL,11,Furged the council to reject the plans.
OL,13,FShe described them as hugely
OL,14,Fcontroversial and said Bewl Water is
OL,15,Fthe most important piece of water in
OL,16,Fthe South East.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772132672
OL,3,CPlans to turn reservoir into a
OL,4,C'holiday resort' rejected by planners
OL,6,F"This plan would threaten the rowing
OL,7,Ffacilities at Bewl", Emily said ahead
OL,8,Fof the planning decision. "Along with
OL,9,Fthe unique habitats that exist there
OL,10,Fand damage the chances that local
OL,11,Frowers can follow in my footsteps.
OL,13,F"Wealden Council need to take a long
OL,14,Fhard look at these plans ` and listen
OL,15,Fto local people and the
OL,16,Fenvironmentalists defending the future
OL,17,Fof this stunning piece of our
OL,18,Fcountryside.
OL,20,F"It was hugely important in helping me
OL,21,Freach the heights that I have."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@SO]pD@[OUuD@AOU|D@AOU}D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772132672
OL,3,CPlans to turn reservoir into a
OL,4,C'holiday resort' rejected by planners
OL,6,FHowever, councillors did go against
OL,7,FWealden's own planning officers, who
OL,8,Fhad recommended the application be
OL,9,Fallowed.
OL,11,FIn their reports, officers said the
OL,12,Fscheme would provide 'valuable tourism
OL,13,Ffacilities', and benefit the economy
OL,14,Fof Bewl Water.
OL,16,FIt would also, officers said, allow
OL,17,Ffor the upgrade of water sport
OL,18,Ffacilities at the site.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772132672
OL,3,CPlans to turn reservoir into a
OL,4,C'holiday resort' rejected by planners
OL,6,FThey wrote: "There is no doubt that
OL,7,FBewl Water is a tourist destination in
OL,8,Fits own right and is a major reason
OL,9,Ffor people to visit this part of the
OL,10,Fregion.
OL,12,F"The importance of Bewl Water to the
OL,13,Fregion's tourism industry is long
OL,14,Festablished and the activities,
OL,15,Ffacilities and events available at
OL,16,FBewl are constantly improving to
OL,17,Frespond to visitor's needs and demand.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772132672
OL,3,CPlans to turn reservoir into a
OL,4,C'holiday resort' rejected by planners
OL,6,F"The proposals will provide more
OL,7,Fflexibility in the length of time
OL,8,Fspent within the Bewl Estate, which in
OL,9,Fturn will encourage greater spending
OL,10,Fboth on site and within the
OL,11,Fsurrounding local area."
OL,13,FThere is still the possibility of
OL,14,Fappeal by those behind the plans and
OL,15,Fthe developers behind the application
OL,16,Fhave been contacted for comment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
